---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for AutoWarehouse by Intellica.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
          AutoWarehouse is a product of Intellica (a PiA Group company). We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about how we collect and use data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Cookies & Analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          We use <span class="text-slate-300">Google Analytics 4</span> with
          <span class="text-slate-300">Google Consent Mode v2</span> to understand how visitors use our site. This helps us improve the experience.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 glass-card rounded-xl p-5 space-y-3">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-white">Before you consent</div>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">Analytics scripts load but do not store cookies or collect personal data. Google receives anonymous, cookieless signals used only for aggregated modeling.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-white">If you accept cookies</div>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">Google Analytics stores first-party cookies to recognize returning visitors, measure session duration, and attribute traffic sources. IP addresses are anonymized.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-white">If you decline cookies</div>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">No analytics cookies are stored. Your choice is remembered in your browser's local storage so you are not asked again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          You can change your cookie preference at any time by clearing your browser's local storage for this site. Under GDPR and similar regulations, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          For questions about privacy, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@intellica.net" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">info@intellica.net</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
